 can be performed at both sides of 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

.
 If 
\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

 is at or close to the boundary, however, one may need to employ a nonsymmetric
 stencil (such as 
\begin_inset Formula $[0,1,2,3,4]$
\end_inset

